fr.ign.cogit.geoxygene.spatialrelation.api

Interface RelationExpression

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AchievementExpression
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ThresholdExpression

    public interface RelationExpression
    Assessing a relation may require a condition to be specified, i.e. the RelationExpression. This condition may refer to a threshold (e.g. two features are near if their relative distance is less than 10m), to other relations (e.g. two features are aligned if they are near and parallel) or to other elements like an intersection matrix template.
    Author:
    GTouya
